01:34:22.529 --> 01:34:24.572
1947. What is that?

01:34:24.656 --> 01:34:26.198
- 19 years.
19 years...

01:34:26.283 --> 01:34:28.909
Williams, Thomas.
- Yeah, over here.

01:34:31.288 --> 01:34:33.539
- Paxon, Edward.
- Yeah.

01:34:34.750 --> 01:34:37.668
What you got? Board of Education.

01:34:37.753 --> 01:34:40.422
