01:43:11.650 --> 01:43:13.276
Zihuatanejo.

01:43:13.360 --> 01:43:15.278
Zi...what?

01:43:15.362 --> 01:43:17.405
Zihuatanejo.

01:43:17.489 --> 01:43:19.574
It's in Mexico.

01:43:21.369 --> 01:43:23.579
A little place on the Pacific Ocean.

01:43:24.831 --> 01:43:27.207
